( Yes,I know I'm a bit late. Had to go to an Early Mother's Day Party for my Mom. If I missed something then someone give me a dingle, please.)


* Iron Raptor growled at Plintissa's answer, she was surrendering to the Preds?! She couldn't believe her hearing mechanisms, why in on earth would a Maximal want to do that?
She growled as she looked over at Prowl, this was turning out to be a pretty sour day!
Iron Raptor opened her com-link to Plintissa again.*

" You can't be serious! Come back to base and we can talk about this, there's no reason that you should be turning yourself in to the Preds...is there?"

* She growled as she left her intercom open for Plintissa to answer, oh please don't let her say that she had betrayed them or worse!
Iron Raptor sighed with concern, she hadn't known Plintissa for long but she knew enough to hope that she hadn't betrayed them. Or so she wished to think.*
